description: while loop with generated accumulator should execute exactly 4 times.
law: (= (with [i 0 acc {a}] (do (while (< i 4) (begin (set! acc (+ acc {b})) (set! i (+ i 1)))) acc)) (+ {a} (* {b} 4)))
